price: Të dy kopshtet jepnin frutat e veta, pa u munguar asgjë dhe bëmë që midis tyre të rridhte një lumë.
arabic: كِلۡتَا ٱلۡجَنَّتَيۡنِ ءَاتَتۡ أُكُلَهَا وَلَمۡ تَظۡلِم مِّنۡهُ شَيۡـٔٗاۚ وَفَجَّرۡنَا خِلَٰلَهُمَا نَهَرٗا

version.title: Albanian Translation - Hasan Nahi
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Albanian by Hasan Nahi, published by Albanian Institute of Islamic Thought and Civilization, printed in 2006.

meta.transliteration: kil'tā al-janatayni ātat ukulahā walam taẓlim min'hu shayan wafajjarnā khilālahumā naharan
translations: And We caused to gush forth
